Big Brother on Monday changed the rules concerning Head of House lounge. Biggie, after Trikytee emerged as Head of House asked him to pick a deputy. Trikytee chose Laycon as his deputy. However, unlike previous weeks, the Head of House is not allowed to spend the night in the lounge. The Deputy Head of House is also the only guest allowed into the lounge. Biggie said: “The Deputy Head of House is not allowed to sleep in the HoH lounge “The Head of House is also the only guest allowed in the room.”